e=diary22>{{cite news |title=Bond 22 Pre-Production Diary (22)|work=[[MI6.co.uk]] |date=2007-12-30 |url=http://www.mi6.co.uk/sections/articles/bond_22_preprod_diary22.php3?t=&s=articles |accessdate=2007-12-31}}</ref> but Forster decided Amalric gave a pitiful quality.<ref name=pity/>
